_sText:
This is an update to my 2023 map: cs_docks_source_new, which is a remake of a cut Counter-Strike map for Counter-Strike: Source.

Why am I uploading this separately instead of updating? Well...

That's because last time I updated cs_mansion_source to cs_mansion_2025, it didn't show up in the "Updated" tab of the Gamebanana page, so nobody really played it, that's a bummer, if that's how it's going to work, and considering this also has a different file name... Then, i'll be uploading a separate update.

New to this update:

-Improved bot / hostage nav considerably, it is not perfect, but they don't get stuck 24/7 like the 2023 version at least.
-Moved hostage rescue zone to be in the tunnel in order to make rescuing hostages less of a hassle, before, it was nearly impossible considering the default time is about 2 minutes.
-Cubemaps are now a thing, yeah, surprised it wasn't before.
-Made some small things more like the original.
-Slight optimization improvements.
-Improved 3D Skybox.

Also check out cs_mansion_2025:
https://gamebanana.com/mods/398586
